In general, while these libraries provide quite similar functionalities. there are differences between them and these differences can beâ€¦ See More summarized in two main points: (1) Numpy does not support all algebraic functions in depth while Scipy does (2) Numpy has a faster processing speed compared to Scipy. As a result, you should always try to see if Numpy can support what you want to do. In cases using Numpy is not enough to solve your problem, let's explore Scipy. #python #numpy #scipy #difference
